4.2 Physiology ‚Üí Strategy

A plan is only as good as the operator‚Äôs physiological readiness.

4.3 Medicine ‚Üí Engineering

Homeostasis mirrors closed-loop control systems.

4.4 Stress ‚Üí Leadership

Understanding stress curves helps allocate people to roles they can sustainably handle.

4.5 Energy ‚Üí Creativity

Cognitive output depends on metabolic availability.

